Simple tcp-socket server, that can broadcast incoming messages to connected sockets.

Start server with:

# Default host is 'localhost'
# Default port is 46969

$ ruby chat_runner <host> <port>

In new console:

$ telnet <host> <port>

To quit telnet, press Shift+Ctrl+] and type 'quit'.

